  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nI think the logs would be nicer if we have a dedicated space between the message title and the key-values associated with `slog`. \r\n\r\nAn example of this format is in geth. \r\n\r\n```\r\nINFO [07-26|12:31:47.821] Maximum peer count                       ETH=25 LES=0 total=25\r\nINFO [07-26|12:31:47.826] Starting peer-to-peer node               instance=Geth/v1.9.0-unstable-78d90c47/linux-amd64/go1.12.3\r\nINFO [07-26|12:31:47.826] Allocated trie memory caches             clean=256.00MiB dirty=256.00MiB\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis issue involves changing the format of the `slog::Logger`. Hopefully a single change in `main.rs` will propagate this format through the codebase :).",
